post_text:
To: All Parents, Staff and Community Members

This to remind you that there is a Strategic Planning meeting scheduled for this evening at 7:00 pm at the RiverWinds Community Center. All members of the West Deptford community are invited to attend. The focus of this evening's discussion will be on the district's "Strengths and Challenges".
Please note that attendance at the first meeting is not required in order to participate.
We hope you are able to attend.

Steve Crispin
